OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cold and quite cloudy start
OL,6,Fwith some frost. Then it will be a dry
OL,7,Fand increasingly sunny day, but
OL,8,Ffeeling cooler than recent days.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FIt will stay dry throughout
OL,11,Fthe evening and overnight. Clear skies
OL,12,Fat first, but high cloud spreading in
OL,13,Ffrom the west later. Overnight frost
OL,14,Fdeveloping.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FAfter a chilly start with
OL,17,Fovernight frost it will be another dry
OL,18,Fand bright day and feeling a bit
OL,19,Fmilder again, especially towards the
OL,20,Fnorth coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
