OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and bright spells on Sunday and
OL,7,FMonday, staying mostly dry but with
OL,8,Fthe occasional spell of rain. Dry
OL,9,Fstart Tuesday but becoming windier as
OL,10,Frain spreads east later.
